<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 02 at 3:19AM PST  by NWS Elko</headline>
<description>...Very cold temperatures for northern Elko county this morning...
Temperatures will drop to around 15 below to 25 below zero this
morning. Even colder wind chills expected. This combination of
weather elements may lead to hypothermia or frostbite. Ensure you
take the proper precautions by dressing warmly.
Visit www.weather.gov/elko for the latest weather information.</description>
